  "state_prompts": [
    "## State: START\n- **Description:** Navigate to Pea River CrowdFiber page\n- **Triggers:**\n\t1. If it is on the chrome homescreen\n- **Actions:**\n\t1. Go to https://peariver.crowdfiber.com/front_end word for word\n\t2. TERMINATE AT THIS POINT",
    "## State: ADDRESS_BAR\n- **Description:** If on the Pea River page\n- **Triggers:**\n\t1. If you see 'Please enter your address below'\n- **Actions:**\n\t1. FOLLOW THESE INSTRUCTIONS CLOSELY\n\t2. Type `%address%` into the input field\n\t3. Type `%zip_code%` into the input field\n\t4. Click the 'Service Type' dropdown, press down key and enter\n\t5. Click the 'Go' button\n\t6. TERMINATE AT THIS POINT",
    "## State: CONFIRM_ADDRESS\n- **Description:** Confirm address location\n- **Triggers:**\n\t1. If you see 'Verify that the marker below is the correct location for your address'\n- **Actions:**\n\t1. Scroll down\n\t2. Click the 'Next' button\n\t3. TERMINATE AT THIS POINT",
    "## State: INTERNET_AVAILABLE\n- **Description:** Service available - enter contact info\n- **Triggers:**\n\t1. If you see 'Pea River is in your neighborhood. Order now!'\n- **Actions:**\n\t1. Scroll to put this contact information in the form\n\t2. Type `%email%`\n\t3. Type `%name_f%`\n\t4. Type `%name_l%`\n\t5. Type `%phone_num%`\n\t6. Click the 'Next' button\n\t7. TERMINATE AT THIS POINT",
    "## State: SERVICEABLE\n- **Description:** Build your bundle\n- **Triggers:**\n\t1. If you see 'Build your bundle'\n- **Actions:**\n\t1. TERMINATE AT THIS POINT\n- **End State:** serviceable_with_plans",
    "## State: NO_SERVICE\n- **Description:** Service not available\n- **Triggers:**\n\t1. If you see 'Aww shucks! Our service isn't available.'\n- **Actions:**\n\t1. TERMINATE AT THIS POINT\n- **End State:** no_service"
  ],
